\c 19 Kuparadzwa kweJerusaremu kunofananidzwa nechirongo chakaputsika 19 1 Zvanzi naJehovha, "Enda undotenga chirongo chakaumbwa no muumbi wehari, unavamwe vakuru vavanhu navamwe vakuru vavapristi; 2 ipapo uende kumupata womwanakomana waHinomi, uripo pavanopinda pa WLN e-WW, \I'VdIV‘7,‘Sed-po Mashoko andichakuudza; 3 uti, ‘Inzwa shoko raJehovha, imi madzimambo aJudha navagere Jerusaremu,' zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsiraeri, `Tarirai, ndichauyisa zvakaipa pamusoro
